																																										<p>On our Classic account type, the spread starts from 1 pip plus any due swaps. On our Edge account type, spread from 0 pips plus any due swaps, and a commission of 7 usd per round turn lot.</p>
																																							</div>
											</div>
																					<div class="question-area">
												<span class="question bold">When is Swap applied?</span>
												<div class="answer-wrapper">
																																										<p>Swap is applied each day that the trade is kept open at 23:59 GMT+2 (server time) each day. The Swap fee is applied triple on Wednesdays (for FX and Metals) to compensate for the weekend. Other asset classes will be charged on Friday.</p>
																																							</div>
											</div>
																					<div class="question-area">
												<span class="question bold">How is Swap calculated relative to my trade?</span>
												<div class="answer-wrapper">
																																										<p>To calculate the swap of a trade it would be:</p><p>Swap Rate x Number of Lots x Number of Nights = Swap to be applied to the trade</p>
																																							</div>
											</div>
																					<div class="question-area">
